rows.label: qst201001_msg0001
rows.name:
It seems the false information
has not yet spread.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0002
rows.name:
The more time it takes, the
more the damage will expand.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0003
rows.name:
We have no time to spare.
I'm counting on you.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0004
rows.name:
It seems the false information
is spreading well in the city.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0005
rows.name:
With this, the Core Crystal hunters
will surely take the bait!

rows.label: qst201001_msg0006
rows.name:
The capture unit is already
prepared. I request the support
of the Mercenary Group.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0007
rows.name:
I thank you for dispatching
the Mercenary Group.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0008
rows.name: We are ready to deploy at any moment.

rows.label: qst201001_msg0009
rows.name:
There is no time. I ask that you all
also move to the operation area.
